   DEBUG: 2026-03-13 17:58:04,782:      pdf_renderer.py:  470: printSegment: | 
   DEBUG: 2026-03-13 17:58:04,783:      pdf_renderer.py:  470: printSegment: Config
   DEBUG: 2026-03-13 17:58:04,784:      pdf_renderer.py:  470: printSegment:  | pydantic-settings, python-dotenv | Type-safe environment variable management |
   DEBUG: 2026-03-13 17:58:04,784:      pdf_renderer.py:  470: printSegment:  
   DEBUG: 2026-03-13 17:58:04,785:      pdf_renderer.py:  470: printSegment: | 
   DEBUG: 2026-03-13 17:58:04,785:      pdf_renderer.py:  470: printSegment: Frontend
   DEBUG: 2026-03-13 17:58:04,786:      pdf_renderer.py:  470: printSegment:  | React 18, TypeScript | Component-based UI with type safety |
   DEBUG: 2026-03-13 17:58:04,786:      pdf_renderer.py:  470: printSegment:  
   DEBUG: 2026-03-13 17:58:04,786:      pdf_renderer.py:  470: printSegment: | 
