   DEBUG: 2026-03-13 17:58:04,811:      pdf_renderer.py:  470: printSegment: What is Kite Connect?
   DEBUG: 2026-03-13 17:58:04,812:      pdf_renderer.py:  470: printSegment: Kite Connect is Zerodha
   DEBUG: 2026-03-13 17:58:04,812:      pdf_renderer.py:  470: printSegment: '
   DEBUG: 2026-03-13 17:58:04,815:      pdf_renderer.py:  470: printSegment: s official REST API platform that allows developers to build trading applications. It
   DEBUG: 2026-03-13 17:58:04,816:      pdf_renderer.py:  470: printSegment: provides endpoints for authentication, portfolio data, order placement, market data, and more.
   DEBUG: 2026-03-13 17:58:04,816:      pdf_renderer.py:  470: printSegment: API Endpoints Used
