   DEBUG: 2026-03-13 17:58:04,819:      pdf_renderer.py:  470: printSegment: Generates Zerodha OAuth login URL |
   DEBUG: 2026-03-13 17:58:04,819:      pdf_renderer.py:  470: printSegment:  
   DEBUG: 2026-03-13 17:58:04,820:      pdf_renderer.py:  470: printSegment: | 
   DEBUG: 2026-03-13 17:58:04,820:      pdf_renderer.py:  470: printSegment: kite.generate_session()
   DEBUG: 2026-03-13 17:58:04,821:      pdf_renderer.py:  470: printSegment:  | POST | Exchanges request token for
   DEBUG: 2026-03-13 17:58:04,821:      pdf_renderer.py:  470: printSegment: access token |
   DEBUG: 2026-03-13 17:58:04,821:      pdf_renderer.py:  470: printSegment:  
   DEBUG: 2026-03-13 17:58:04,822:      pdf_renderer.py:  470: printSegment: | 
   DEBUG: 2026-03-13 17:58:04,822:      pdf_renderer.py:  470: printSegment: kite.holdings()
   DEBUG: 2026-03-13 17:58:04,822:      pdf_renderer.py:  470: printSegment:  | GET | Fetches all delivery equity holdings |
   DEBUG: 2026-03-13 17:58:04,823:      pdf_renderer.py:  470: printSegment:  
   DEBUG: 2026-03-13 17:58:04,823:      pdf_renderer.py:  470: printSegment: | 
   DEBUG: 2026-03-13 17:58:04,824:      pdf_renderer.py:  470: printSegment: kite.profile()
   DEBUG: 2026-03-13 17:58:04,824:      pdf_renderer.py:  470: printSegment:  | GET |
   DEBUG: 2026-03-13 17:58:04,825:      pdf_renderer.py:  470: printSegment: Gets user profile (name, ID) |
   DEBUG: 2026-03-13 17:58:04,825:      pdf_renderer.py:  470: printSegment:  
   DEBUG: 2026-03-13 17:58:04,825:      pdf_renderer.py:  470: printSegment: | 
   DEBUG: 2026-03-13 17:58:04,826:      pdf_renderer.py:  470: printSegment: kite.place_order()
   DEBUG: 2026-03-13 17:58:04,826:      pdf_renderer.py:  470: printSegment:  | POST | Places a market sell order |
   DEBUG: 2026-03-13 17:58:04,827:      pdf_renderer.py:  470: printSegment:  
   DEBUG: 2026-03-13 17:58:04,827:      pdf_renderer.py:  470: printSegment: | 
   DEBUG: 2026-03-13 17:58:04,827:      pdf_renderer.py:  470: printSegment: kite.invalidate_access_token()
   DEBUG: 2026-03-13 17:58:04,828:      pdf_renderer.py:  470: printSegment:  | DELETE | Logs out / invalidates session |
   DEBUG: 2026-03-13 17:58:04,828:      pdf_renderer.py:  470: printSegment: API Pricing
