   DEBUG: 2026-03-13 17:58:04,829:      pdf_renderer.py:  470: printSegment: |------|------|----------|
   DEBUG: 2026-03-13 17:58:04,830:      pdf_renderer.py:  470: printSegment:  
   DEBUG: 2026-03-13 17:58:04,830:      pdf_renderer.py:  470: printSegment: | 
