   DEBUG: 2026-03-13 17:58:04,833:      pdf_renderer.py:  470: printSegment: | Connect | ₹500/month | Adds live WebSocket streaming, historical candle data |
   DEBUG: 2026-03-13 17:58:04,834:      pdf_renderer.py:  470: printSegment: 7. Authentication Flow
   DEBUG: 2026-03-13 17:58:04,834:      pdf_renderer.py:  470: printSegment: OAuth Login Sequence
   DEBUG: 2026-03-13 17:58:04,834:      pdf_renderer.py:  470: printSegment: | Step | Description |
   DEBUG: 2026-03-13 17:58:04,835:      pdf_renderer.py:  470: printSegment:  
   DEBUG: 2026-03-13 17:58:04,835:      pdf_renderer.py:  470: printSegment: |------|------------|
   DEBUG: 2026-03-13 17:58:04,836:      pdf_renderer.py:  470: printSegment:  
   DEBUG: 2026-03-13 17:58:04,836:      pdf_renderer.py:  470: printSegment: | 
   DEBUG: 2026-03-13 17:58:04,836:      pdf_renderer.py:  470: printSegment: Step 1
   DEBUG: 2026-03-13 17:58:04,837:      pdf_renderer.py:  470: printSegment:  | User clicks 
   DEBUG: 2026-03-13 17:58:04,837:      pdf_renderer.py:  470: printSegment: "
   DEBUG: 2026-03-13 17:58:04,837:      pdf_renderer.py:  470: printSegment: Connect Zerodha
   DEBUG: 2026-03-13 17:58:04,838:      pdf_renderer.py:  470: printSegment: "
   DEBUG: 2026-03-13 17:58:04,838:      pdf_renderer.py:  470: printSegment:  in the frontend |
   DEBUG: 2026-03-13 17:58:04,838:      pdf_renderer.py:  470: printSegment:  
   DEBUG: 2026-03-13 17:58:04,839:      pdf_renderer.py:  470: printSegment: | 
   DEBUG: 2026-03-13 17:58:04,839:      pdf_renderer.py:  470: printSegment: Step 2
   DEBUG: 2026-03-13 17:58:04,840:      pdf_renderer.py:  470: printSegment:  | Frontend
   DEBUG: 2026-03-13 17:58:04,840:      pdf_renderer.py:  470: printSegment: navigates to 
   DEBUG: 2026-03-13 17:58:04,840:      pdf_renderer.py:  470: printSegment: /api/auth/login
   DEBUG: 2026-03-13 17:58:04,841:      pdf_renderer.py:  470: printSegment:  → backend redirects to Kite login page |
   DEBUG: 2026-03-13 17:58:04,841:      pdf_renderer.py:  470: printSegment:  
   DEBUG: 2026-03-13 17:58:04,842:      pdf_renderer.py:  470: printSegment: | 
   DEBUG: 2026-03-13 17:58:04,842:      pdf_renderer.py:  470: printSegment: Step 3
   DEBUG: 2026-03-13 17:58:04,843:      pdf_renderer.py:  470: printSegment:  | User enters Zerodha ID +
   DEBUG: 2026-03-13 17:58:04,844:      pdf_renderer.py:  470: printSegment: Password + TOTP on Kite
   DEBUG: 2026-03-13 17:58:04,844:      pdf_renderer.py:  470: printSegment: '
   DEBUG: 2026-03-13 17:58:04,845:      pdf_renderer.py:  470: printSegment: s login page |
   DEBUG: 2026-03-13 17:58:04,845:      pdf_renderer.py:  470: printSegment:  
   DEBUG: 2026-03-13 17:58:04,845:      pdf_renderer.py:  470: printSegment: | 
   DEBUG: 2026-03-13 17:58:04,846:      pdf_renderer.py:  470: printSegment: Step 4
   DEBUG: 2026-03-13 17:58:04,846:      pdf_renderer.py:  470: printSegment:  | Kite redirects to 
   DEBUG: 2026-03-13 17:58:04,847:      pdf_renderer.py:  470: printSegment: /api/auth/callback?request_token=xxx&status=success
   DEBUG: 2026-03-13 17:58:04,847:      pdf_renderer.py:  470: printSegment:  |
   DEBUG: 2026-03-13 17:58:04,848:      pdf_renderer.py:  470: printSegment:  
   DEBUG: 2026-03-13 17:58:04,848:      pdf_renderer.py:  470: printSegment: | 
   DEBUG: 2026-03-13 17:58:04,848:      pdf_renderer.py:  470: printSegment: Step 5
   DEBUG: 2026-03-13 17:58:04,849:      pdf_renderer.py:  470: printSegment:  | Backend calls 
   DEBUG: 2026-03-13 17:58:04,849:      pdf_renderer.py:  470: printSegment: generate_session()
   DEBUG: 2026-03-13 17:58:04,850:      pdf_renderer.py:  470: printSegment:  to exchange request token → access token |
   DEBUG: 2026-03-13 17:58:04,851:      pdf_renderer.py:  470: printSegment:  
   DEBUG: 2026-03-13 17:58:04,851:      pdf_renderer.py:  470: printSegment: | 
   DEBUG: 2026-03-13 17:58:04,851:      pdf_renderer.py:  470: printSegment: Step 6
   DEBUG: 2026-03-13 17:58:04,853:      pdf_renderer.py:  470: printSegment:  | Backend stores access token in
   DEBUG: 2026-03-13 17:58:04,853:      pdf_renderer.py:  470: printSegment: memory, redirects user to frontend with 
   DEBUG: 2026-03-13 17:58:04,854:      pdf_renderer.py:  470: printSegment: ?connected=true
   DEBUG: 2026-03-13 17:58:04,854:      pdf_renderer.py:  470: printSegment:  |
   DEBUG: 2026-03-13 17:58:04,855:      pdf_renderer.py:  470: printSegment:  
   DEBUG: 2026-03-13 17:58:04,855:      pdf_renderer.py:  470: printSegment: | 
   DEBUG: 2026-03-13 17:58:04,855:      pdf_renderer.py:  470: printSegment: Done
   DEBUG: 2026-03-13 17:58:04,857:      pdf_renderer.py:  470: printSegment:  | Access token valid for ~24 hours. No
   DEBUG: 2026-03-13 17:58:04,857:      pdf_renderer.py:  470: printSegment: TOTP needed for subsequent API calls. |
   DEBUG: 2026-03-13 17:58:04,858:      pdf_renderer.py:  470: printSegment: Key Detail: TOTP is Only Needed at Login
   DEBUG: 2026-03-13 17:58:04,865:      pdf_renderer.py:  470: printSegment: The TOTP (Time-based One-Time Password) from Google Authenticator is required only during the OAuth login
   DEBUG: 2026-03-13 17:58:04,867:      pdf_renderer.py:  470: printSegment: step. Once the access token is obtained, all API calls (fetching holdings, placing orders) work without any additional
   DEBUG: 2026-03-13 17:58:04,868:      pdf_renderer.py:  470: printSegment: authentication until the token expires.
   DEBUG: 2026-03-13 17:58:04,868:      pdf_renderer.py:  470: printSegment: Daily Login Required
   DEBUG: 2026-03-13 17:58:04,873:      pdf_renderer.py:  470: printSegment: Access tokens are invalidated by Zerodha between 6:00–8:30 AM daily. Per SEBI exchange regulations, users must
   DEBUG: 2026-03-13 17:58:04,873:      pdf_renderer.py:  470: printSegment: log in manually once per day. There is no refresh token mechanism available for standard API users.
   DEBUG: 2026-03-13 17:58:04,874:      pdf_renderer.py:  470: printSegment: 8. Core Features
