   DEBUG: 2026-03-13 17:58:04,990:      pdf_renderer.py:  470: printSegment:  Legal Considerations
   DEBUG: 2026-03-13 17:58:04,990:      pdf_renderer.py:  470: printSegment: Important: This Tool is for Personal Use Only.
   DEBUG: 2026-03-13 17:58:04,991:      pdf_renderer.py:  470: printSegment:  
   DEBUG: 2026-03-13 17:58:04,996:      pdf_renderer.py:  470: printSegment: PanicSell is designed and intended for personal
   DEBUG: 2026-03-13 17:58:04,998:      pdf_renderer.py:  470: printSegment: portfolio management on a single Zerodha account. It must not be used to trade on behalf of others,
   DEBUG: 2026-03-13 17:58:04,999:      pdf_renderer.py:  470: printSegment: offered as a service, or distributed commercially.
   DEBUG: 2026-03-13 17:58:05,000:      pdf_renderer.py:  470: printSegment: SEBI 2025 Regulatory Framework Compliance
   DEBUG: 2026-03-13 17:58:05,000:      pdf_renderer.py:  470: printSegment: | Requirement | How PanicSell Complies |
   DEBUG: 2026-03-13 17:58:05,001:      pdf_renderer.py:  470: printSegment:  
   DEBUG: 2026-03-13 17:58:05,001:      pdf_renderer.py:  470: printSegment: |-------------|----------------------|
   DEBUG: 2026-03-13 17:58:05,002:      pdf_renderer.py:  470: printSegment:  
   DEBUG: 2026-03-13 17:58:05,003:      pdf_renderer.py:  470: printSegment: | Personal use, single account | Connects to
   DEBUG: 2026-03-13 17:58:05,004:      pdf_renderer.py:  470: printSegment: one Zerodha account only; no multi-user support |
   DEBUG: 2026-03-13 17:58:05,004:      pdf_renderer.py:  470: printSegment:  
   DEBUG: 2026-03-13 17:58:05,005:      pdf_renderer.py:  470: printSegment: | 2FA / TOTP mandatory | Enforced by Zerodha
   DEBUG: 2026-03-13 17:58:05,005:      pdf_renderer.py:  470: printSegment: '
   DEBUG: 2026-03-13 17:58:05,006:      pdf_renderer.py:  470: printSegment: s login — users must
   DEBUG: 2026-03-13 17:58:05,006:      pdf_renderer.py:  470: printSegment: enter TOTP at OAuth login |
   DEBUG: 2026-03-13 17:58:05,007:      pdf_renderer.py:  470: printSegment:  
   DEBUG: 2026-03-13 17:58:05,008:      pdf_renderer.py:  470: printSegment: | Manual trigger (not automated) | All sells require explicit user action (button click +
   DEBUG: 2026-03-13 17:58:05,008:      pdf_renderer.py:  470: printSegment: confirmation) |
   DEBUG: 2026-03-13 17:58:05,008:      pdf_renderer.py:  470: printSegment:  
   DEBUG: 2026-03-13 17:58:05,009:      pdf_renderer.py:  470: printSegment: | Daily manual login required | Token expires daily; user must re-authenticate each morning |
   DEBUG: 2026-03-13 17:58:05,009:      pdf_renderer.py:  470: printSegment:  
   DEBUG: 2026-03-13 17:58:05,011:      pdf_renderer.py:  470: printSegment: | No
   DEBUG: 2026-03-13 17:58:05,011:      pdf_renderer.py:  470: printSegment: exchange registration needed | Personal-use tools with manual triggers don
   DEBUG: 2026-03-13 17:58:05,012:      pdf_renderer.py:  470: printSegment: '
   DEBUG: 2026-03-13 17:58:05,012:      pdf_renderer.py:  470: printSegment: t require exchange approval |
   DEBUG: 2026-03-13 17:58:05,013:      pdf_renderer.py:  470: printSegment:  
   DEBUG: 2026-03-13 17:58:05,014:      pdf_renderer.py:  470: printSegment: | No data
   DEBUG: 2026-03-13 17:58:05,015:      pdf_renderer.py:  470: printSegment: redistribution | Portfolio data is displayed only to the authenticated user locally |
   DEBUG: 2026-03-13 17:58:05,015:      pdf_renderer.py:  470: printSegment:  
   DEBUG: 2026-03-13 17:58:05,017:      pdf_renderer.py:  470: printSegment: | Order frequency thresholds | Batch
   DEBUG: 2026-03-13 17:58:05,018:      pdf_renderer.py:  470: printSegment: sell is a single user action; does not approach algo-trading OPS limits |
   DEBUG: 2026-03-13 17:58:05,019:      pdf_renderer.py:  470: printSegment: What is NOT Permitted
