   DEBUG: 2026-03-13 17:58:05,034:      pdf_renderer.py:  470: printSegment: Create a new app (Personal plan, free)
   DEBUG: 2026-03-13 17:58:05,034:      pdf_renderer.py:  470: printSegment:  3 
   DEBUG: 2026-03-13 17:58:05,034:      pdf_renderer.py:  470: printSegment: Enter your Zerodha Client ID (your trading user ID)
   DEBUG: 2026-03-13 17:58:05,035:      pdf_renderer.py:  470: printSegment:  4 
   DEBUG: 2026-03-13 17:58:05,035:      pdf_renderer.py:  470: printSegment: Set Redirect URL to 
   DEBUG: 2026-03-13 17:58:05,035:      pdf_renderer.py:  470: printSegment: http://localhost:8000/api/auth/callback
   DEBUG: 2026-03-13 17:58:05,036:      pdf_renderer.py:  470: printSegment:  5 
   DEBUG: 2026-03-13 17:58:05,036:      pdf_renderer.py:  470: printSegment: Note the generated 
   DEBUG: 2026-03-13 17:58:05,036:      pdf_renderer.py:  470: printSegment: API Key
   DEBUG: 2026-03-13 17:58:05,037:      pdf_renderer.py:  470: printSegment:  and 
   DEBUG: 2026-03-13 17:58:05,037:      pdf_renderer.py:  470: printSegment: API Secret
   DEBUG: 2026-03-13 17:58:05,037:      pdf_renderer.py:  470: printSegment: Step 2: Backend
   DEBUG: 2026-03-13 17:58:05,038:      pdf_renderer.py:  470: printSegment: cd panicsell/backend
   DEBUG: 2026-03-13 17:58:05,038:      pdf_renderer.py:  470: printSegment: python3 -m venv venv
   DEBUG: 2026-03-13 17:58:05,038:      pdf_renderer.py:  470: printSegment: source venv/bin/activate
   DEBUG: 2026-03-13 17:58:05,039:      pdf_renderer.py:  470: printSegment: pip install -r requirements.txt
   DEBUG: 2026-03-13 17:58:05,039:      pdf_renderer.py:  470: printSegment: # Create .env with your credentials
   DEBUG: 2026-03-13 17:58:05,040:      pdf_renderer.py:  470: printSegment: cp .env.example .env
   DEBUG: 2026-03-13 17:58:05,040:      pdf_renderer.py:  470: printSegment: # Edit .env: KITE_API_KEY=xxx, KITE_API_SECRET=xxx
   DEBUG: 2026-03-13 17:58:05,040:      pdf_renderer.py:  470: printSegment: # Start the server
   DEBUG: 2026-03-13 17:58:05,041:      pdf_renderer.py:  470: printSegment: uvicorn app.main:app --reload --port 8000
   DEBUG: 2026-03-13 17:58:05,041:      pdf_renderer.py:  470: printSegment: Step 3: Frontend
   DEBUG: 2026-03-13 17:58:05,042:      pdf_renderer.py:  470: printSegment: cd panicsell/frontend
   DEBUG: 2026-03-13 17:58:05,042:      pdf_renderer.py:  470: printSegment: npm install
   DEBUG: 2026-03-13 17:58:05,042:      pdf_renderer.py:  470: printSegment: npm run dev
   DEBUG: 2026-03-13 17:58:05,043:      pdf_renderer.py:  470: printSegment: Step 4: Use the App
   DEBUG: 2026-03-13 17:58:05,043:      pdf_renderer.py:  470: printSegment:  1 
   DEBUG: 2026-03-13 17:58:05,044:      pdf_renderer.py:  470: printSegment: Open 
   DEBUG: 2026-03-13 17:58:05,044:      pdf_renderer.py:  470: printSegment: http://localhost:5173
   DEBUG: 2026-03-13 17:58:05,044:      pdf_renderer.py:  470: printSegment:  in your browser
   DEBUG: 2026-03-13 17:58:05,045:      pdf_renderer.py:  470: printSegment:  2 
   DEBUG: 2026-03-13 17:58:05,045:      pdf_renderer.py:  470: printSegment: Click 
   DEBUG: 2026-03-13 17:58:05,045:      pdf_renderer.py:  470: printSegment: "
   DEBUG: 2026-03-13 17:58:05,046:      pdf_renderer.py:  470: printSegment: Connect Zerodha
   DEBUG: 2026-03-13 17:58:05,046:      pdf_renderer.py:  470: printSegment: "
   DEBUG: 2026-03-13 17:58:05,046:      pdf_renderer.py:  470: printSegment:  and log in with your credentials + TOTP
   DEBUG: 2026-03-13 17:58:05,047:      pdf_renderer.py:  470: printSegment:  3 
   DEBUG: 2026-03-13 17:58:05,047:      pdf_renderer.py:  470: printSegment: View your portfolio, select stocks, and sell as needed
